We have completely FREE calls and global voice Call in TruePhone Call .
In TruePhone Call , you don't have to need a sim card or a number , all you need is a stable network.

100% FREE CALL  100% Free & global phone call free. No contract, no hidden fees.

Free credits
New users will get a bonus of 300 credits. Make your first TruePhone Call now! By the way,You can get free credits from daily lucky spin and playing online games or view some ads.

International calls
TruePhone Call allows you to make free international calls to anyone in the world, even if your friends do not have an Internet connection. We makes it available to make phone calls from any device with a network , which helps you make calls when traveling abroad.

No Phone Number Needed
You can make stable calls without a mobile phone number and only need the Internet , we support both WIFI and cellular data networks..

Clear & Stable Calling  Server worldwide to ensure high quality phone calls with clarity and stability!

⭐TruePhone Call can reach any mobile or landline number in more than 230+ countries or regions! Use TruePhone Call to make global calls possible. Meet me, meet friends, and meet people anywhere on this voice calling app.

Our calling rates are cheaper than most international calling apps. You can see the final cost of each call in the cost history. Also, the balance never expires.
